displayName: Lake Paelis "Dungoo's Hideout, Ruins of the Crimson Bloodline

parameters:
\c[2][Crimson Bloodline Ruins: South]\c[0]South]: South]: South] has been recorded in the
portal.

Here it is. I've heard a lot about Remi being a
very scary monster, so please be careful...

Edda, it's difficult for me to say, but she...
came here on her own and went to Remi's place.

I didn't know the reason, but it didn't feel like
she was being deceived or anything like that. It
was a firm determination.
I'm sorry, but in the end, I couldn't help her.

No... This is also my responsibility... Ah, let's
consider the quest complete.

If I hadn't infiltrated here, I wouldn't have
known anything. Thank you so much for doing
various things in my place.

Hmm... I couldn't quite understand everything,
but... I guess there's no helping it this time.
※助けるを選んで勝った場合

I defeated Remi... but Noah... disappeared just
like that.

I didn't know the reason, but she came here on her
own and went to Remi's place.

I tried to help her by force if necessary... but
it didn't work.

Ah... Perhaps... I was already captivated by
Remi...

But... this is also my responsibility... Ah, let's
consider the quest complete.

If I hadn't infiltrated here, I wouldn't have
known anything. Thank you so much for doing
various things in my place.

Hmm... I couldn't quite understand everything,
but... I guess there's no helping it this time.
text_indicator : Ruins of the Crimson Bloodline: South
ボスを撃破することで、ストーンを制御できる

after being able to control this Nest Stone with
magic\C[1]!

Stone? If you release it, nearby enemies will
attack.
Released the control of the Nest Stone!

\C[1]The nearby enemies became docile!
